# Development Roadmap

## Phase 1: Core Foundation ✅ (Completed - Q4 2024)

### 1.1 Multi-LLM Provider Support ✅
- **OpenAI Integration**: GPT-4o, GPT-3.5-turbo support
- **Anthropic Integration**: Claude-3-Opus, Claude-3-Sonnet support  
- **Google Integration**: Gemini-1.5-Pro-Latest support
- **Ollama Integration**: Local model support (Llama3, Mistral, CodeLlama)
- **LM Studio Integration**: On-premises deployment support
- **vLLM/Custom Support**: Flexible deployment options
- **Dynamic Provider Switching**: Environment-based configuration

### 1.2 RAG System Architecture ✅
- **Document Processing Pipeline**: PDF, DOCX, TXT, URL support
- **Vector Database**: LanceDB with hybrid search capabilities
- **Agent System**: RAG, Reasoning, and Research Team agents
- **Knowledge Management**: Comprehensive document handling
- **Session Management**: Persistent conversation history

### 1.3 User Interfaces ✅
- **Web Dashboard**: Modern HTML/CSS/JS interface (port 8000)
- **AGUIApp UI**: Python-based developer interface (port 8501)
- **CLI Interface**: Interactive command-line tool
- **Real-time Features**: File upload, URL processing, streaming responses
- **Advanced Controls**: Reasoning mode toggle, session management

### 1.4 API & Integration ✅
- **FastAPI Backend**: RESTful API with OpenAPI documentation
- **Session CRUD**: Complete session management API
- **Health Monitoring**: Health check endpoints
- **Error Handling**: Comprehensive exception management
- **Logging System**: Structured logging and debugging

### 1.5 Infrastructure ✅
- **Containerization**: Docker support for all services
- **Orchestration**: Kubernetes deployment manifests
- **Local Development**: Docker Compose setup
- **Infrastructure as Code**: Terraform configurations
- **CI/CD Pipeline**: GitHub Actions workflows

